OL,7,FThousands of people in Wales are at
OL,8,Frisk of losing their rights due to
OL,9,Ffailures in the EU Settlement Scheme
OL,10,F(EUSS), according to a report.
OL,12,FThe Senedd's Equality and Social
OL,13,FJustice Committee warns in its latest
OL,14,Ffindings that EU citizens living in
OL,15,FWales could risk losing rights,
OL,16,Fincluding access to work, housing,
OL,17,Fbenefits, and education, because of
OL,18,Fthe scheme's "lack of awareness" and
OL,19,F"complexity".
