OL,7,FThe EUSS is the UK Government's system
OL,8,Fwhich EU citizens must use to apply to
OL,9,Fstay in the UK after Brexit.
OL,11,FIn an interview with ITV Cymru Wales,
OL,12,FTony Fernandes Da Silva, who came to
OL,13,Fthe country more than 20 years ago,
OL,14,Fsaid he would not come to the UK today.
OL,16,FDa Silva, who is originally from
OL,17,FPortugal and runs a cafe in Ebbw Vale,
OL,18,Fcurrently holds indefinite leave to
OL,19,Fremain in the UK.
