OL,7,FSpeaking about the immigration system,
OL,8,FMr Da Silva said it doesn't benefit
OL,9,Fpeople who "want to put in the work
OL,10,Flike myself."
OL,12,F"It is very complex," he added. "Last
OL,13,Fyear, I tried to apply for British
OL,14,FCitizenship - which I can - but it's
OL,15,Fso difficult, the actual questions you
OL,16,Fhave to go through and study, you've
OL,17,Feven got British people who would not
OL,18,Fbe able to pass it."
OL,20,FMr Da Silva said his time in the UK
OL,21,Fhas been a challenge.
