OL,7,F"It's been very hard. Obviously you
OL,8,Fnever expect it to be easy but I am
OL,9,Fwilling to go through the hard work.
OL,10,FBut today, no matter how hard you
OL,11,Fwork, you are basically just paying
OL,12,Fbills."
OL,14,FThe report states that frequent
OL,15,Fchanges and digital-only processes
OL,16,Fwithin the immigration system create
OL,17,Fbarriers for vulnerable people.
