OL,7,FMr Da Silva said he has seen this
OL,8,Ffirst hand: "Everything is online. I'm
OL,9,Fnot the brightest but I can do it.
OL,10,FOthers find themselves lost. You could
OL,11,Fbe a very good manual labourer when it
OL,12,Fcomes to work force but when it comes
OL,13,Fto technology you might not.
OL,15,F"The way it's going they are getting
OL,16,Fpenalised by it through no fault of
OL,17,Ftheir own."
