OL,7,F"The worry will always be there as to
OL,8,Fwhether they will be able to settle
OL,9,Fwith indefinite leave to remain or
OL,10,Fwhether they will be told they have to
OL,11,Fleave, go back to their home country.
OL,12,FAnd that is always on the back of
OL,13,Ftheir mind."
OL,15,FA spokesperson from the Home Office
OL,16,Fsaid the scheme had "allowed millions
OL,17,Fof EU citizens and their eligible
OL,18,Ffamily members with the immigration
OL,19,Fstatus to continue living and working
OL,20,Fin the UK after Brexit."
