OL,7,FBut the Senedd Committee warns that
OL,8,Fthe scheme possesses "hallmarks of
OL,9,FWindrush," as it places the burden of
OL,10,Fproof on individuals to prove
OL,11,Fresidency when they may not have the
OL,12,Fnecessary documentation.
OL,14,FThe report comes almost five years
OL,15,Fafter Brexit. During which, more than
OL,16,F131,000 applications have been made
OL,17,Ffrom Wales, with over 113,000
OL,18,Fsuccessful outcomes, totalling 3.6% of
OL,19,Fthe Welsh population.
