OL,7,FHowever, the true number of people
OL,8,Feligible to apply is not known.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Chair of the Senedd's
OL,11,FEquality and Social Justice Committee,
OL,12,FJenny Rathbone MS, said: "The
OL,13,Fconsequences of not obtaining
OL,14,Fpermission to stay is dire."
OL,16,F"We add our voice to the chorus of
OL,17,Fothers sounding the alarm about the
OL,18,Fcomplexity of the system as people
OL,19,Fremain unaware that they need to apply.
