OL,7,FShe added: "We hope a future Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment will continue to
OL,9,Fproactively target support towards
OL,10,Fvulnerable groups who we know are
OL,11,Flikely to slip through the net and be
OL,12,Funaware of the need to apply. We urge
OL,13,Fa future Senedd committee to continue
OL,14,Four work, holding the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fto account so that no EU citizen in
OL,16,FWales is left behind."
