OL,7,FMeanwhile, a Home Office spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "No one who has already gained
OL,9,Fsettlement in the UK will have their
OL,10,Fstatus changed.
OL,12,F"The EU Settlement Scheme has provided
OL,13,Fmillions of EU citizens and their
OL,14,Feligible family members with the
OL,15,Fimmigration status to continue living
OL,16,Fand working in the UK after Brexit."
